        dc:modified        "2025-01-03T09:53:44.628Z"^^xsd:dateTime;
        skos:altLabel      "interdisciplinary approaches"@en;
        skos:definition    "Interdisciplinary studies address specific real-world problems, bringing people and ideas together from different disciplines to collectively frame a problem, agree on a methodological approach, and analyse data in an integrated manner (Adapted from Hammer and Söderqvist (2001) and Stock and Burton (2011), and references therein, in Gill et al., 2022)."@en;
